{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_26","type":"agent_message","text":"The first patch didn’t take effect because the `typeReached` guard is too late in the execution path: the failure happens while `DefaultPlexusContainer` is still constructing Guice bindings, before any `org.apache.maven.project.DefaultMavenProjectBuilder` logic is reached. I’m tightening the next patch around that earlier container path and, to avoid one-by-one churn, I’m mirroring the known Guice primitive-converter registrations used elsewhere in this repo."}}
